content_description: A person wearing a backpack walks through a long, arched stone tunnel lit by wall lamps.

High.reason: Initial entry into the tunnel with clear movement and a strong perspective shift as the camera follows closely.

Medium.reason: Steady walking through a well-lit section of the arched tunnel, maintaining a consistent pace.

Low.reason: Walking through a darker, more shadowed part of the tunnel where visual details are obscured and motion feels slower.
